{"tid":1804193,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"可以在海外成立類似Russell Tribunal或China Tribunal的民間法庭去審判黑警的罪行嗎？","createTime":"2019-12-30T22:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T22:19:55.000Z","uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"96bc0f84fc23ca21ae5910da87b062f7f8fb2cfd","tid":1804193,"uid":293282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T22:19:55.000Z","msg":"可以在海外成立類似Russell Tribunal或China Tribunal的民間法庭去審判黑警的罪行嗎？<br />\n<br />\n羅素法庭（Russell Tribunal），由哲學家羅素成立用以審判美軍越戰罪行的民間法庭：<br />\n<br />\n簡介: <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BD%97%E7%B4%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E7%25BD%2597%25E7%25B4%25A0%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%25BA%25AD&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=1ab9616b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%BD%97%E7%B4%A0%E6%B3%95%E5%BA%AD</a><br />\n<br />\n中國法庭（China Tribunal），審判中國活摘器官一案所成立的民間法庭，最近於2019年6月宣佈中國政府罪名成立：<br />\n<br />\n新聞: <a href=\"https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewelinaochab/2019/06/17/the-china-tribunal-pronounced-its-verdict-on-organ-harvesting-in-china/#2c6427832eeb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.forbes.com%2Fsites%2Fewelinaochab%2F2019%2F06%2F17%2Fthe-china-tribunal-pronounced-its-verdict-on-organ-harvesting-in-china%2F%232c6427832eeb&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=82963ab5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.forbes.com/sites/ewelinaochab/2019/06/17/the-china-tribunal-pronounced-its-verdict-on-organ-harvesting-in-china/#2c6427832eeb</a><br />\n成員: <a href=\"https://chinatribunal.com/who-we-are/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinatribunal.com%2Fwho-we-are%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=fc4a0f41\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinatribunal.com/who-we-are/</a><br />\n中文版判詞簡要: <a href=\"https://chinatribunal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/SHORT-FORM-of-THE-CHINA-TRIBUNAL-JUDGEMENT-Chinese.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchinatribunal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F07%2FSHORT-FORM-of-THE-CHINA-TRIBUNAL-JUDGEMENT-Chinese.pdf&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=0ca6addd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://chinatribunal.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/SHORT-FORM-of-THE-CHINA-TRIBUNAL-JUDGEMENT-Chinese.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n其它民間法庭:<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.irantribunal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.irantribunal.com&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=79703a32\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.irantribunal.com</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.tribunal1965.org/en/tribunal-1965/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribunal1965.org%2Fen%2Ftribunal-1965%2F&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=c69e07f3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.tribunal1965.org/en/tribunal-1965/</a>   <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.tribunalonmyanmar.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tribunalonmyanmar.org&d=BC5i8YeQzBb8hGTgU6tpJhckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=7008b431\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.tribunalonmyanmar.org</a>"}]}